Package com.catenax.tdm.scenario

Interface TestDataScenarioListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
TestDataScenarioBaseListener, TestDataScenarioExecutor
public interface TestDataScenarioListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by TestDataScenarioParser.
